' | Aktor: Pemilik          | ✓ Bagian 4, BR-10    | ✓ Karakteristik Pengguna | ✓ |
' | UC_Login                | ✓ Otentikasi         | ✓ F-01: Modul Autentikasi | ✓ |
' | UC_Transaksi            | ✓ BR-07, BR-08       | ✓ F-02: Transaksi Multi-Lini | ✓ |
' | UC_Bayar                | ✓ BR-07              | ✓ F-02: Pembayaran DP/Lunas | ✓ |
' | UC_Retur                | ✓ BR-09              | ✓ F-02: Pembatalan & Retur | ✓ |
' | UC_Inventaris           | ✓ Manajemen Stok     | ✓ F-03: Manajemen Gudang | ✓ |
' | UC_BOM                  | ✓ HPP berbasis BOM   | ✓ F-03: Bill of Materials | ✓ |
' | UC_HPP                  | ✓ Perhitungan HPP    | ✓ F-03: HPP Otomatis | ✓ |
' | UC_StatusPesanan        | ✓ Job Tracking       | ✓ F-04: Manajemen Pesanan | ✓ |
' | UC_Arsip                | ✓ Arsip Desain       | ✓ F-04: Lokasi Arsip | ✓ |
' | UC_Limbah               | ✓ BR-06              | ✓ F-05: Waste Management | ✓ |
' | UC_Absen                | ✓ Manajemen SDM      | ✓ F-06: Kehadiran | ✓ |
' | UC_Kasbon               | ✓ Pengelolaan Kasbon | ✓ F-06: Data Kasbon | ✓ |
' | UC_Gaji                 | ✓ BR-03, BR-04       | ✓ F-06: Penggajian Cerdas | ✓ |
